== Amezruy n Tefsut n Yimazighen : D acu yedhran ? ==
 
 
[Tafsut n 1980 deg Tmurt n Leqbayel d tin ay ikecmen deg umezruy (ttarix) n tmazight d win n Ldzayer akk-n ma tella. Deg wussan-nni, dhrant adtas n tghawsiwin s tghawla, d tid ay yuraren ddurh d ameqran deg tikli i lmend n westeârhef s tmazight deg tmurt-is. Yelha ma nessawel-d ghef way-n yedhran deg Tefsut-nni akk-n ad nefhem xir tidyanin-a. Adhris-a ay d-nuwey d tukkist (extrait) seg "Weghmis n Tedyanin n Tmurt n Leqbayel" ay yura Rachid Chaker deg tallit-nni u yeffegh-d deg tesghunt (revue) n "Les Temps Modernes" (udttunen 432-433, Yunyuz-Ghuct 1982), akk d tesghunt Tafsut.]
 
 
Ass n lh’edd, 9 Meghres 1980 :
Tasdawit n Tizi Wezzu tella tesâa imir-n sin n yiseggasen d wezgen seg wasmi ay tettwaldi yernu yufa-d lh’al yagi tga tlata yisundilen (grèves) imeqranen, aneggaru deg-sen d win ay d-yellan deg gar 17 Tuberh d 13 Nwemberh 1979. Asunded-nni gan-t ghef wugur n ugenses idetti (représentation authentique) n yinelmaden sdaxel n tesdawit. Akabar n Tirni n Weslelli Aghelnaw (FLN) yella la d-yeqqar dakk-n inelmaden ara yesseh’rhasen akk-n ad gen isundilen-a d "imesmazighen" (berbéristes) negh d imarhksiyen imazighen (u llan qqaren-asen "Bougiots").
 
Seg yimir-n, iselmaden ay llan ttwalin-ten d imarhksiyen, llan ur ten-ttaznen ara gher Tizi Wezzu, wanag ttaznen-ten gher tesdawit n Sedttif. Ma d iselmaden idzayriyen ay yeghran deg Frhansa llan ttqaraâen-ten u tikkwal ssagaden-ten. Yagi, deg way-n iâeddan, adtas n tikkal ur jjin ara ad d-ilint tmeskanin tidelsanin (manifestations culturelles) tidelsanin timazighin deg Tizi Wezzu. Ur jjin ara Aït Menguellet negh Yidir ad cnun, menâen tamezgunt (pièce de théâtre) n "2000 n yiseggasen n Ṭ̣dtrad" ay llan tturaren-tt-id s teqbaylit.
 
Kra n wussan uqbel ma yusa-d Mouloud Mammeri gher tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu akk-n ad d-yeg asarag-is, snedtdhen yinelmaden inazalen (affiches) deg yigherban akk-n ad d-xebbren ghef way-a. Anemhal n tesdawit (recteur), ghas ma yella ur as-yeâjib ara lh’al, yeqbel ad d-yili usarag-nni imi d aseqqamu (comité) n ugharam (cité) n Oued Aïssi ay d-yelhan s tigin n usarag-a yernu aseqqamu-a testeârhef yes-s tedbelt (administration). D acu kan, adtas n yinazalen ay d-yettwasghersen. Deg yidh n wass n lh’edd d letniyen (ghef ttnac n yidh), yeghra-as-d yiwen i Mouloud Mammeri, yenna-as dakk-n d netta ay d anemhal n tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu u yenna-as dakk-n asarag-nni-ines yebdtel. 
 
 
Ass n letniyen 10 Meghres 1980
Azekka-nni taṣ̣ebh’it, Mouloud Mammeri yesteqsa, u d Mass Arab, anemhal (directeur) n tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu s timmad-is ay as-yennan dakk-n maci d netta ay as-d-yeghran yernu asarag-ines ur yettwamneâ, ur yettuwexxer. Ghef tizi n ttnac n wass, Mouloud Mammeri yeqleâ seg Ldzayer, yedda id-s Salem Chaker d yiwen n unehharh iqeddcen deg CRAPE, la tteddun gher Tizi Wezzu. Mi uwdhen gher Dreâ Ben Xedda, ghef jjuj, yeh’bes-iten yiwen n wuggug (barrage) n yibulisen (uggug nidhen yella yegguni-ten deg Buxalfa).
 
Sdeffir ma walan lekwaghedh-is, ibulisen uwyen Mouloud Mammeri gher uwali n Tizi Wezzu, u d netta ay as-d-yennan s yimi-s dakk-n asarag-ines (conférence) gher "yisefra iqdimen n teqbaylit" yettwamneâ imi ay-a "yezmer ad d-yawi ccwal", am wakk-n ay as-yenna ad yeffegh seg Tizi Wezzu imir-nni kan. Yugh lh’al, awali yekcef-d ula d win ay iwekkel akk-n ad as-d-igher i Mammeri deg yidh-nni u ad as-yini dakk-n asarag-is yettwamneâ. Wagi d Mass Merabtene, d anemhal (directeur) n COUS. Akk-a, Mammeri yeqqel yezsra dakk-n anemhal n tesdawit ula ay t-yegren deg way-nni. Yugh lh’al, anemhal n tesdawit akk d umaru amatu (secrétaire général) qqlen nnan-as i Mammeri dakk-n ay-nni yekka-d nnig n tezmert-nsen. Ghef rhrhebâa d wezgen n tmeddit, llan ugar n 1000 n medden ara yettrhajun melmi ara yebdu usarag-nni. Mi zsran dakk-n yettwamneâ, bdan la ten-id-ttalin wurfan, yernu ssefran ad gen timlilit i uzekka-nni, 11 Meghres, ghef 9 n tṣ̣ebh’it.
 
 
Ass n ttlata 11 Meghres
Inelmaden gan tameskant-nsen (manifestation) tamezwarut deg yizenqan n Tizi Wezzu. Ghef ttesâa n tṣ̣ebh’it ay mlalen u gar n 10:15 d 12:15, gar n 500 d 700 n yinelmaden ay yelh’an deg yizenqan n Tizi Wezzu, zzin-d sin iberdan ghef yizenqan imeqranen n temdint. Tikli teh’bes sdat n Useqqamu Aghelnaw Agherfan (CNP) n FLN, sdat n twilayt u sdat n tesnawit (lycée) n temdint, u llan refden tih’ucay ay deg d-uran "Idles amazigh : idles agherfan", "Awali, Aseqqamu aghelnaw agherfan, asarag n Mammeri yettwamneâ ?", "H’ebset aqmadh n yedles". Uran-d daghen s tefrhensist : "Ad yeghli weqmadh" (répression), "Awali, Aseqqamu aghelnaw agherfan d iqettalen". Ma s tmazight uran-d "Tamazight d tameslayt-nnegh", "Ad nerrezs wala ad neknu", "Neâya deg lbadtel".
 
Imezsla (ssrabes) n weqmadh (respression) llan h’edrhen s wadtas dinna : ibulisen, ijaderhmiyen d yisexsayen (pompiers), d acu kan, ur d-giren ara iman-nsen. Kullec yeh’bes deg temdint yernu medden llan la d-ttdhillin seg dttwaqi n yexxamen. Medden amzun ddan u fkan-asen lh’eqq i yinelmaden-nni, maca ur d-sbanen ara lebghi-nsen akk-n ad ttekkin negh ad âawnen inelmaden. D acu, llant kra n temgharin nnant-asen d "arrac ijehlen". Deg tmeddit n wass-nni, mlalen yiselmaden idzayriyen n tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu u uran-d adhris (texte) n yiwet n tsakbabt (pétition), adhris-nni gan-t d tabrhat yeldin i uneghlaf (ministre) n usselmed aâlayan. Deg wedhris-nsen, iselmaden ur qbilen ara imi ay yettwamneâ usarag (conférence) n umeddakel-nsen deg tesdawit, u sh’erhsen i wakk-n ad tettuqader lh’erhma n tesdawit (ur qbilen ara imi ara d-keccmen yibulisen gher daxel n tesdawit ...), a m wakk-n ssuttren ad tili tlelli n wawal ladgha deg way-n yerzan idles d yiles amazigh. Tabrhat-nni zemlen-tt (stenyan-tt) rhebâin n yiselmaden (rhebâa yimuren ghef xemsa seg yiselmaden idzayriyen yellan qeddcen deg tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu).
 
 
Ass n larhebâa 12 Meghres 1980
Agraw amatu (assemblée générale) n yinelmaden n Tizi Wezzu yura-d yiwet n "tebrhat yeldin i Uselway n Tegduda". Tabrhat-nni ssuffghen-d seg-s luluf n tsukan (copies) u ferqen-tent deg wadtas n yimukan (Ldzayer, Bumerdas, atg.). Tabrhat-a yettwarun s yiles ur nqesseh’ ara adtas d tin ay deg d-bedren yinelmaden ay-n d-yeqqar werkawal aghelnaw (charte nationale). Daghen, inelmaden bedren-d deg tebrhat-nsen akk ay-n yedhran deg wussan-nni nnan-d dakk-n iles d yedles imazighen ttalasen ad ttusnernin, am wakk-n d-ssuttren dakk-n tamazight ad teqqel d iles aghelnaw wis sin deg tmurt.
 
Deg Ldzayer tamaneght, medden yeslan s way-n ara idherrun deg Tizi Wezzu, banen-d amzun ur uminen ara, bitt llan kra kra nnan-d dakk-n ay-a d lekdeb akk yernu ur uminen ara ula s Mouloud Mammeri dakk-n yella. D acu kan, llan kra n medden, qlilit, llan bghan ad gen tameskant (tamesbanit) deg wezniq !
 
 
Ass n lexmis 13 Meghres 1980
Iselmaden n Usudu n Tussniwin Tudmisin (institut des Sciences économiques) n Ldzayer tamaneght) asmi ay zsran s lexbar, gan tasakbabt (pétition) ay fkan i weghlif (ministère) akk-n ad d-sseknen dakk-n ur qbilen ara amnaâ n usarag-nni (conférence) n Mammeri. Adhris-a zemlen-t (stenyan-t) rhebâin n yiselmaden, meh’sub tlata n yimuren ghef rhebâa seg yiselmaden idzayriyen (gar-asen wid iqeddcen deg PAGS [akabar amesdukli (parti communiste)] d wid iqeddcen deg tedbelt (administration)]. Deg webrid, gar Budwaw d Tizi Wezzu, amur ameqran deg yigalisen (tiplakin) akk d tseddariyin (abribus) uran deg-sent s ssbigha : "Tugdut", "Aït Ahmed deg tmurt !", "H’ebset assenger n yedles !", "FLN amaynut d afaci", "Akk d inmeglayen" (opposants). Tira-a uran-tent deg yidh n 12 d 13 Meghres. Medden walan daghen tira am tigi deg Tizi Wezzu akk d yiberdan yettalin gher tuddar deg Tmurt n Leqbayel. Adabu yeâredh ad yeffer akk tira-nni s tghawla s ssbigha tamellalt negh tawerhdit, deg wass n lexmis, 13 Meghres. Ass-nni daghen ay d-yeffegh umagrad (article) amezwaru deg lberhrhani ghef way-n ara idherrun deg Tizi Wezzu. Wa d amagrad awezlan ay d-yeffghen deg weghmis afrhensis n Libération, yeh’ka-d ay-n yedhran s tidet deg wass n 11 Meghres. (Mebla ccek, d ay-n ay yejjan akk lejnas ad d-rren lwelha-nsen gher tedyanin-a !).
 
 
Ass n ljemâa 14 Meghres 1980
Medden bdan la ttmeslayen ghef tira-nni u mxallafen lerhyuy-nsen fell-asen.
 
 
Ass n ssebt 15 Meghres 1980
Terza yiwet n tfagla (délégation) n yinelmaden i tikkelt tamezwarut gher tselwit (présidence) u tejja-n dinna tabrhat yeldin i uselway. D A. Benhabyles ay ten-yemmugren, iban-d yewhem maca ur d-yesban ara taâdawt-ines. Inelmaden sseknen-as-d amek ay tettwaru tmazight (s tfinagh) u yenna-d dakk-n yefka tira-nni i Uselway (?). Deg temlilit-ines tis snat akk d yinelmaden ay d-yesban addud-ines (position).
 
 
Ass n lh’edd 16 Meghres 1980
Deg Ldzayer, medden la ttmeslayen dakk-n tella yiwet n tewriqt n FFS ay yettwaferqen ghef yinelmaden deg wussan-nni (yugh lh’al, d tin ay d tawriqt tis tlata ara yefreq ukabar-a deg setta n wayyuren ineggura). Tawriqt-a tessawal-d ghef tedyanin-nni n Tizi Wezzu u tenna-d dakk-n 2000 n yinelmaden ay yettekkan deg tmeskant-nni (tamesbanit) n 11 Meghres (yili ay-a ur iṣ̣eh’h’a).
 
Deg Tmurt n Leqbayel, ass n lh’edd 16, letniyen 17 d wass n ttlata 18 Meghres, medden gan timeskanin (timesbaniyin) deg Larhebâa n Ayt Yiraten, deg Yiâezszsugen akk d Ain Lh’emmam. Deg Larhebâa n Ayt Yiraten, medden qqimen la tteddun deg yizenqan tlata n wussan, wa sdeffir wa. Adtas seg wid yettekkan deg tmeskanin-a d ilmezsyen (inelmaden n tesnawiyin [lycéens], atg.), akk d kra n yigerdan d tlawin (amur ameqran deg-sent d timgharin). Ḍrant tghawsiwin yessewhamen. Deg Larhebâa n Ayt Yiraten, medden kecmen gher lkazirhna u h’ettmen iserdasen (iâsekrhiyen) ad d-ffghen seg-s s yicedttidhen n waddal (sport) (imi ay llan la ttgen addal) i wakk-n ad ttekkin yid-sen deg tmeskant ghef yiles amazigh. Ula d amghiwan (lmir) h’ettmen-t ad d-yeffegh, u ad yezwir i ṣ̣ṣ̣ef u ad d-yini "Ad ddren Yimazighen".
 
Deg yal amkan, medden rzsan jjaj d yigalisen (tiplakin) n lbenyanat n ddula u uran fell-asen isekkilen (lh’urhuf) n tfinagh. Deg Yiâezszsugen, yiwen n ubulis yusa-d ad yennagh medden imi ay rzsan yiwen n ugalis n FLN, dgha smaren fell-as acabcaq n ssbigha tazewwaght. Imsenza (ttejjarh) ghelqen tih’una-nsen maca kra nnan-d dakk-n d medden ay ten-ih’ettmen ad ghelqen.
 
 
Ass n letniyen 17 Meghres 1980
Daniel Junqua yellan la iqeddec d anemyaru (correspondant) deg weghmis n "Le Monde", yedda gher Tizi Wezzu u yebda la yesteqsay inelmaden d yiselmaden. Yeâredh ad yesteqsi daghen kra n yemdhebbren, maca ur yessawedh ara (anemhal n tesdawit [recteur] ulac-it, atg.). Deg wass n 19 Meghres, yeffegh-d umagrad (article) amezwaru deg Le Monde u yeh’ka-d ghef lumurh akk-n dhrant (mebla azeyyed wala assenqes).
 
Deg tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu, inelmaden d yiselmaden la ssawalen ghef wakk ay-n yedhran. Llan kra bghan ad d-sseknen dakk-n ur qbilen ara ad ad d-gren iman-nsen yikabaren (partis) n tenmegla (oppisition) deg temsalt-a u ad âerdhen ad sqedcen tidyanin-a deg leṣ̣lah’-nsen, d acu kan, rran-ten deg rrif yernu jjan ay-n akk-n llan bghan ad t-gen. Tameddit-nni, Ferhat Mhenni, acennay n terbaât Imazighen Imula iga abaraz (gala) deg telmessit (foyer) n yinelmaden deg Yih’esnawen. H’edrhen azal n 1000 n yinelmaden, gar-asen anemhal (directeur) n COUS, Merabtene, yellan yeskerh yernu llan la smesxiren yes-s yinelmaden. Abaraz-nni yeqqel d timlilit ay yes d-sseknen yinelmaden dakk-n ur qbilen ara aqmadh (respression) n ddula. Timlilit-a teqqel mechurhet imi ay sqerdcen yinelmaden s lejherh ghef kra n temsal tisertiyin (politiques) am tuqqla n Aït Ahmed d Boudiaf. Arezki About yellan iqeddec deg unegmi (laboratoire) n tesdawit, yessawel-d ghef yiwet n tewriqt ay n FUAA ay d-sâeddan s ddaw n tewwurt n texxamt-is.
 
 
Ass n ttlata 18 Meghres 1980
