== 1980 : Abeddel ameqran ==

 
"Tafsut n Yimazighen" n 1980 d yiwet seg tedyanin tisertiyin (politiques) timeqranin akk deg Ldzayer timziregt (indépendante).
 
Uqbel, tamsalt n tmazight tella tenkerh-itt ddula yernu imassanen (savants) llan qqnen fell-as allen, negh ur ttwalin-tt d tamsalt ur nesâi azal meghghren, d tin yeqqnen s afulklurh. D acu kan, asmi ay d-dhrant tedyanin n 1980, tamsalt-a deg yiwen webrid kan tban-d u yegget fell-as wawal.
 
Timeskanin (timesbaniyin) akk d yimenghiyen ay d-yellan gar medden d yighallen n ddula deg wakk timiwa n Tmurt n Leqbayel akk d Ldzayer tamaneght gar Meghres n 1980 d Mayyu n 1981 sseknen-d dakk-n wid yessutturen tamazight ur llin d aggagen (intellectuels) imeâzulen, wanag d ay-n yerzan u bghan-tt akk wid yessawalen tamazight deg Ldzayer.
 
"Tafsut n Yimazighen" d tin ay d-yemlan dakk-n medden ukin-d u bdan la ttxemmimen ad d-nedtqen, ad d-ssiwlen i yiman-nsen ghef way-n bghan deg yiwet n tmurt anda ddula tella tebgha ad d-tessken dakk-n kullec deg-s yeddukkel. Uqbel, tasertit (politique), tasnakta (idéologie) d yedles llan s ddaw n umunupul n ddula yernu d tamendhawt (consitution) ay as-idhemnen ay-a. U deg way-n yerzan iles, ulac kra n tlelli deg tmurt imi seg wasmi ay tuwey Ldzayer azarug-ines (indépendance), akk timendhawin n tmurt qqarent-d dakk-n d "taârhabt ay d iles aghelnaw unṣ̣ib (national et officiel) n tmurt".
 
Idhrisen n llsas (textes fondamentaux) n tmurt d nitni sskanayen-d s lejherh dakk-n d ddula kan ay yettalasen ad tedttef asselghu (information) u ad t-tesseddu s yiles ay as-yehwan. Tighawsiwin banent ugar mi ara ngher tizzwariyin (préambules) ay d-uran i tmendhawin (constitutions), d tid-nni umi qqaren "irkawalen ighelnawen" (chartes nationales).
 
D acu kan, seg wasmi ay tâedda Tefsut n 1980, lejyal n yelmezsyen bdan la d-sskanayen dakk-n ugin inedhfaren-nni (dogmes) ay yettwah’ettmen fell-asen.
 
D ljil s lekmal-is n yelmezsyen, d imezdaghen akk n Tmurt n Leqbayel ay d-yekkren u ssuttren "asteârhef s yiles amazigh" d u ad asen-tettunefk "tlelli n wawal".
 
D tadyant yesâan izsuran lqayit
 
Assutter n tmazight yesâa izsuran ijehden deg wegdud, d ay-n ara idumen yernu ur yezmir ad yettussusem. Amnaâ n usarag (conférence) n Mouloud Mammeri deg wass n 10 Meghres 1980 d ifedttiwej ay d-yessaghen urfan yellan ffren seg zik-nni. Yagi, deg Tmurt n Leqbayel, medden llan wwan u rran urfan-nsen gher daxel seg tezwara n yiseggasen n 1970. 
 
Tasdawit n Tizi Wezzu, yettwaldin deg 1979, tejbed-d adtas n waggagen, teqqel d amkan anda ay ttemlilin akk wid yeghran deg Tmurt n Leqbayel. Ay-a yurar ddurh deg ussenker n tmeskanin-nni (timesbaniyin). Maca ghas ma yella d tasdawit n Tizi Wezzu ay yeqqimen ach’al n ledwarh la tessedday deg tmeskanin-nni, ay-n ay d-yesnekren medden ur yeqqin ara kan gher temsal taggagin (intellectuelles). Amur ameqran deg yimezdaghen n Tmurt n Leqbayel h’ulfan dakk-n terza-ten temsalt n ussutter n tmazight yernu ttekkan deg tedyanin-nni. Yugh lh’al, seg wasmi ay tuwey Ldzayer azarug-is (indépendance), ula d yiwen wass ur d-llint tmeskanin (timesbaniyin) timeqranin am tid ay d-yellan deg wussan-nni n tefsut. Ama deg Tizi Wezzu, ama deg Bgayet, d ledwarh ay qqimen medden la ttgen timeskanin (timesbaniyin). Ula deg temdinin timecdtuh’in, ffghen-d medden akk-n ad d-sseknen dakk-n ur qbilen ara tikli n ddula (Ain Lh’emmam, Larhebâa n Ayt Yiraten, Dreâ Lmizan, Bughni, Iâezszsugen, Amizsur, Sidi Aic, Aqbu, atg.), ula deg tuddar.
 
Ghas ma yella kra n yimanayen (observateurs) ifrhensisen nnan dakk-n ala deg Tizi Wezzu d tama-ines ay d-llant tedyanin, Tamurt n Leqbayel akk tewlawel, s "tmeqrant", s "tmecdtuh’t". Bitt, tikkwal, kra seg yimenghiyen ay d-yellan deg "tmecdtuh’t" (Bgayet d yeghzer n Ṣṣ̣umam) ugaren wid ay d-yellan deg Tizi Wezzu. Aqmadh (répression) ur yezgil ula d yiwet n tama. Tubiret d Bgayet, ghas ma llan kra ay yettwalin dakk-n txuṣ̣ṣ̣ timmuzgha-nsent, ughent tiytiwin ijehden ugar n tid ay tugh Tizi Wezzu. Akk-n yebghu yili, ghas ma yella kulci yebda-d seg Tizi Wezzu, ddula ur twit ara medden deg-s akk-n ay ten-twet anda nidhen yernu seg 1980 d asawen, teqqel tetth’adar tamdint-a d tmura ay d-iqerben gher-s. 
 
Tamsalt n tmazight dindin kan tefreq u tennul adtas n tmiwa n tmurt n Ldzayer. Yernu d ilmezsyen s umata ay tt-yettnaghen fell-as, dgha d ay-n ay agh-yejjan ad d-nini dakk-n amussu-a (mouvement) d win ara idumen u ad yesâu azal meghghren deg uzekka n tmurt. Ddula teâredh ad tesseddu awal dakk-n wid ay d-yesnekren tamsalt n tmazight d kra n yemdanen ur nemâin, ur nesâi azal yernu "jjmen tallit n Frhansa", maca ay-a ur yelli d tidet, wanag wid yennughen ghef temsalt n tmazight ggten u mezszsiyit.
 
Amur ameqran deg wid irefden tamsalt-a dima llan sâan s ddaw n 25 n yiseggasen deg leâmerh-nsen. Wid yerghan fell-as adtas, amur meghghren deg-sen d inelmaden n tesnawit (lycée), yernu ur ttâeddin ara i âecrin n yiseggasen deg leâmerh. Akk-a ay yella lh’al ama deg tmeskanin (timesbaniyin) n 1980, ama deg wakk tid ay tent-id-idhefren. Akk-a daghen ay yella lh’al deg tmeskanin-nni ay d-yellan deg Nwemberh n 1985 : ixxamen n ccrheâ n Tmurt n Leqbayel h’ekmen s lh’ebs ghef wazal n meyya n yelmezsyen ghef ljal n "ccwal" ay snekren deg yiberdan, akk-n ma llan d inelmaden n tesnawit (lycée). Ljil-a n yelmezsyen d Ldzayer ay ten-yesseghren akk yernu ur ssinen ara Frhansa ... Ghas ma yella nga-as dakk-n wid ay d-yesnekren timeskanin-a (timesbaniyin) d imdanen yeghran s tefrhensist yernu ahat jjmen kra n zzman iâeddan, amek ara d-nessefhem dakk-n ilmezsyen n Tmurt n Leqbayel ay tessgher ddula n Ldzayer ad ddun d wid yebghan ad rren Ldzayer gher deffir ?
 
Yugh lh’al, tasertit-nni (politique) n usseârheb ur tessawedh ara ad d-teqleâ "ay-n ay d-yeqqimen" seg temsalt n tmazight seg Tmurt n Leqbayel wanag d assejhed ay tt-tessejhed. Takti (lfekra) n tmazight tugh akk timiwa n Tmurt n Leqbayel deg lweqt ay deg ddula tella tugi-tt u la tt-tetth’arhab seg lqaâa. D ti ay d tighawsiwin ay wughur yessefk ad d-rren lwelha-nsen wid yesseddayen lumurh n ddula.
 
Amussu (mouvement) n tmazight ur yelli ara daghen yezmer ad yettwarnu, imi ay d-yenker deg yiwet n tallit ay t-iâawnen ghef way-nni, d tallit ay deg ikabaren (partis) uffiren (gar-asen FFS n Aït Ahmed d kra n trebbaâ timecdtuh’in n uzelmadh) gren-d iman-nsen, d acu kan, medden maci d ikabaren-nni ay dhefren wanag ay-n ay ten-yessewlawlen yugar ay-a.
Yugh lh’al, ikabaren n tenmegla (opposition) deg Ldzayer qqimen d uffiren alama ay d tagara n 1988, yernu ula d yiwen wass ur ssawdhen ad rṣ̣un iman-nsen deg wegdud u ad yagh uzsar-nsen deg-s u ad idum, yernu ula d yiwen wass ur gin kra n tigawt (action) ara idumen akk-n ad qablen tasertit (politique) n ddula.
 
Akk ighallen isertiyen (politiques) ay temneâ ddula llan d uffiren, ur zmiren ara ad gen kra ara d-yawin lfayda ibanen, ur llin ara sâan isenfaren (projects) ibanen, llan ttwaqemdhen (réprimer) dima negh sya gher da, dgha ula d yiwet seg trebbaâ-a ur tessawedh ad d-tban, ad tif tiyadh negh ad temneâ seg uqareâ d weqmadh (répression) n yibulisen.
 
Amussu (mouvement) adelsan amazigh yefhem seg tazwara dakk-n ur yessefk ara ad d-yeghli deg snat n tfexxtin : tamezwaurt, ur yessefk ara ad yeqqel d uffir, tis snat, ur yessefk ara ad yeqqim s ddaw tecdhadht n yikabaren (partis). Dgha, wid ay t-id-yesnekren deg yiseggasen n 1980, ssawlen-d s lejherh, zsran-ten medden. Yugh lh’al, mi ara nwali gher ussirem-nsen, gher tmughliwin d uxemmem-nsen, ad nzser dakk-n wid yennughen ghef tmazight glan-d s ubeddel ameqran deg tmurt n Ldzayer, snekren-d tagrawla (révolution) n tidet : medden qqlen zemren ad ssiwlen s lejherh, deg webrid, yernu yettwakcef-d weqmadh-nni (répression) ay tqemmedh ddula n Ldzayer s kra n win ara d-yessiwlen. D ay-a ay yejjan ad d-yekker yiwen n ljil n yimeghnasen (militants) ur nettagad, d wid iwejden ad nnaghen akk d weqmadh n ddula u ad bedden ghef wawal-nsen alama d dtterf. Zik, akk-n ad tessens urfan n medden, ddula tella tettadttaf wid ay d-yessenkaren timeskanin (timesbaniyin) negh th’ebbes medden yettekkan deg trebbaâ ur nelli, negh deg trebbaâ, seg wasmi ay tent-id-sbedden llan yagi deg-sent yemdanen iqeddcen d yighallen n laman, maca, asmi ay d-yekker ljil-a amaynut n yelmezsyen, tighawsiwin qqlent ur la tteddunt ara am wakk-a. Tiâeqqayin n tmazight ghlint u mghint-d deg yal tama, d ay-n ay d-yesnekren adtas n medden, mi tensa tmes da, ad d-tekker anda nidhen. Yeqqel yimenghi iban, yettili-d s lejherh, d imenghi s ljehd n yighil ay yekksen tugdi akk d tsusmi seg wulawen n medden. Yekkes lweh’c-nni izedghen medden zik-nni, deg tallit n Boumediene, asmi ay llan ttxemmimen dakk-n ighallen n ddula llan deg yal amkan. 
 
D acu kan, yessefk daghen ad nzser dakk-n deg 1980, ddula n Ldzayer tella la tettbeddil : tamettant (lmut) n Boumediene tessewlawel akk ddula d werkad ay tella terked-it zik-nni, yernu adabu (autorité) n Chadli Bendjedid ur yejhid ara akk. D ay-a ay yejjan ddula amzun temmehmeh, ur tezsri ara d acu n tikli ara d-tawi akk d tmeskanin-nni (timesbaniyin) n 1980, ladgha imi ula d yiwen wass ur d-llint tedyanin timeqranin am tid-nni yernu tella ddula ur tebni ara fell-asent ad d-ilint. Tlata n wayyuren ay teqqim ddula âerqent-as, tikkelt ad tesseqdec ighil (dgha tiyita ijehden akk d tin n 20 Yebrir, asmi ay mmghen yibulisen ghef tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu), tikkelt, tâerredh ad tessens times, am wasmi ay d-bran i 24-nni n warrac "ay d-yesnekren ccwal" sdeffir ma âeddan deg ccrheâ n laman n ddula). Taggara, ddula tefren ad teqbel tamsalt n tmazight, ad tt-teddem u ad d-telhu id-s akk-n ad tezmer ad tt-teh’kem, yili uqbel tella teffegh-as akk afus. D acu kan, deg tallit-nni n ukukru n ddula, wid ay d-yesnekren amussu (mouvement) amazigh ssawdhen ad d-sseknen dakk-n tamsalt n tmazight tesâa izsuran lqayen deg wegdud : medden gan sin n yisudiden imuta (grèves générales), llant-d adtas n tmeskanin, llan-d adtas n yimenghiyen u qqlen yimenghiyen-nni weârhen u meghghrit ugar sdeffir n 20 Yebrir. Seg wasmi ay tuwey Ldzayer azarug-ines (indépendance), d tikkelt tamezwarut ay deg ara d-kkren yimezdaghen n yiwet n tama s lekmal-is u ssawdhen ad bedden ach’al n ledwarh deg wudem n ddula.
 
S way-a, d imeghnasen (militants) n yedles, amur ameqran deg-sen mezszsiyit, yernu deg tallit-nni tella texdha-ten tsertit (politique) negh akk-n kan ay bdan keccmen deg-s, ssawdhen ad gen ay-n ur igi ula d yiwen n ukabar aserti (parti politique) n menwala ar imir-n : bedden s lejherh deg wudem n ddula yernu idum webdad-nsen alama ay h’ettmen ddula ad testeârhef s temsalt-nsen yernu ad tessenqes seg teqseh’ n weqmadh-ines (répression).
 
1980 : Tadukli n waggagen* d wegdud
 
*intellectuels
 
"Tafsut n Yimazighen" n 1980 tella-d deg yiwet n tallit ay tt-iâawnen akk-n ad d-tili : imeghnasen (militants) n tmazight qqimen la qeddcen azal xmesdtac n yiseggasen deg yedles, ghas s tuffra, imeghnasen yerghan adtas ghef temsal-a bdan la keccmen tasertit (politique) yernu tebda la tettwabnay cwidt, cwidt yiwen n uzsedhdha (réseau) n "yimeghnasen imesmazighen" (amazighistes). Gar way-a d way-n nidhen, Tizi Wezzu tella la tettnerni s tghawla, dgha, sdeffir ma tella d tamdint yeqquren, teqqel d tamdint meghghren deg tama-nni. Deg 1979, tettwaldi tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu, dgha d nettat ay d ssebba ay yejjan Tafsut n 1980 ad d-tagh. Ghas ma yella timeskanin (timesbaniyin) n 1980 maci d aggagen (intellectuels) d yesdawanen (universitaires) kan i yiman-nsen ay tent-igan, maca tildin n tesdawit deg Tizi Wezzu d ay-n yuraren ddurh meghghren deg tmeskanin-a yernu d nettat ay yejjan amussu (mouvement) ad yimghur.
 
Amussu (mouvement) amazigh, asmi ay d-yedtterdheq, yelfa-d d ameqran, xeldhen deg-s akk medden yernu ur iṣ̣eggem ara aṣ̣eggem ay ijehden, dgha d tasdawit ay yuraren ddurh deg usseqâed d usseddu n lecghal n umussu-nni.
 
Ghef way-a, maci deg lbadtel ara tâerredh ddula n Ldzayer ad tessenqes seg ljehd n tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu (imi ur tezmir ara ad tt-tekkes) : akk isenfaren (projets) n wesnerni n tesdawit-a llan ttuwexxaren, sneqsen seg-s inelmaden alama ay d ay-n kan, ttwakksen seg-s yinurar n usselmed s lekmal-nsen yernu iban dakk-n ddula tebgha ad terr tasdawit-a d tarbaât kan n yigherbazen (llakulat) n yisuda (insituts) n usselmed aâlayan, ay deg ur ttilin ara wadtas n yinelmaden u ad ifsusen i weh’kam.
 
Tafsut n 1980 tessken-d daghen dakk-n tella-d tdukli gar waggagen imeghnasen (intellectuels militants) d wegdud deg Tmurt n Leqbayel. Ay-a yesskanay-d ay-n gant trebbaâ deg lgherba seg 1965 alama ay d imir-n d ay-n yeddan d way-n yebgha wegdud, yernu leqdic-nsen yegla-d s laterh d ameqran deg tmetti (société) n Tmurt n Leqbayel.
 
Werjin yewlawel wegdud deg Tmurt n Leqbayel u deg Ldzayer akk akk-n yewlawel asmi ay sdukklen waggagen (intellectuels) ighallen-nsen akk d wegdud, u d ay-a ay yejjan amussu (mouvement) amazigh ad d-iban s lejherh u ad yimghur akk-n ad yagh akk Tamurt n Leqbayel akk d Ldzayer tamaneght u ad yeqqim akk-n ugar n useggas (seg 10 Meghres 1980 ar 19 Meghres 1981).
 
1980 : d tiyita ay d-yejjan laterh 
 
Deg yiseggasen ay d-idhefren tafsut n 1980, nezmer ad nger tamawt dakk-n amussu (mouvement) amazigh yekka ghef snat n talliyin yemgerraden (yemxallafen). Talliyin-a mgerradent ama deg tegnit ay deg d-llant, ama deg tsudist-nsent (stratégie).
 
Tallit n Meghres 1980 ar Ctemberh 1981, nezmer ad as-nsemmi "tallit yeh’man", d tin ay deg yella wadtas n leqdic akk d tmeskanin (timesbaniyin) timeqranin deg webrid (ama deg Tmurt n Leqbayel negh deg Ldzayer tamaneght), timliliyin, inejmuyaâ yemgerraden, timsirin (ddurhus) n tmazight (ama deg Ldzayer negh deg Tmurt). Yugh lh’al, imir-n, wid ay d-yesnekren u sseddan amussu (mouvement) amazigh dindin kan ukin dakk-n timsal n tmagit (identité) tamazight d tid wughur d-rran medden lwelha-nsen yernu adtas n medden ay yewlawlen fell-asent. Akukru n ddula akk d beddu n weskasi (débat) ghef yedles deg tmurt n Ldzayer d ay-n ay yejjan imeghnasen (militants) ad farhsen tagnit u ad sdumen lh’erhs ghef ddula. Yugh lh’al, imeghnasen ssarmen ad teg ddula kra n tghawsa ibanen i tmazight, ad teldi tiwwura u lxerṣ̣um ad teqbel ad tettusselmed tmazight u ad yili unadi fell-as deg tesdawiyin n Tizi Wezzu akk d Ldzayer tamaneght. D ay-a ay yes d-yewâed uneghlaf (lewzir) n usselmed aâlayan n tallit-nni, A. Bererhi.
 
D acu kan, dindin kan teqqel ddula gher weqmadh-ines. Tebda la tferren wid ara tedttef u ad ten-tawey gher lh’ebs (maci d imeghnasen n menwala) i wakk-n ad tesseâreq tikli i umussu (mouvement) amazigh.
 
Asmi ay ifuk useqqamu alemmas n FLN askasi-ines (débat) ghef yedles aghelnaw ay d-yellan gar Yunyu d Yunyuz n 1981, iga-d timeghtusin (résolutions) ghef yedles, dgha tebda tikli n ddula la d-tettban. Ddula tâawed yefren ad tkemmel deg timughliwin-ines tiquranin imi askasi-a yefra-tt-id dakk-n tamagit (identité) tadzayrit d taârhabt-tineslemt. Llan kra n yemdanen seg wid yettekkan deg weskasi-nni, nnan-d dakk-n mazal zemrent ad ilint lemcawrhat ghef temsalt-a (ghas ma yella timughliwin n yemdanen-a llant beâdent s wadtas ghef tid n yimeghnasen [militants] imazighen), d acu kan, d wid yettnaghen ghef tesnakta (idéologie) taârhabt ay yernan deg weskasi-a. Yagi, adtas n yiseggasen seg wasmi ay bdan yemsaârhaben (arabistes) d yemsaârhaben-isenselmen (arabo-islamistes) la keccmen u la ttadttafen akk tisuda (institutions) n tesnakta n ddula, ladgha deg yedles, deg usselmed u deg ukabar (parti) n FLN.
 
Imeghnasen (militants) n tmazight âerdhen tikkelt taneggarut "ad h’erhsen ddula swadda", dgha gren-d tighri i medden, deg wass n 26 Ctemberh, akk-n ad gen asunded amatu (grève générale) u ad ghanzun (boycotter) agherbaz (llakul), d acu kan, tikkelt-nni, medden ur ten-dhfiren ara akk-n yessefk acku, mebla ccek, ur yeffigh ara fell-asen way-nni deg tegnit-nni. Dgha, iban-asen-d i yimeghnasen n tmazight dakk-n ulac d acu ara asen-d-tefk ddula, wanag taneggarut-a la tqeddec akk-n ad yeqqim kullec akk-n yella zik, bitt, tebda la tqeddec akk-n ad tessejhed asseârheb. Ay-a iban-d deg tuqqla (rentrée) gher tesdawit deg 1981, imi ay teâzem ddula ad tesseârheb akk ifurkawen (branches) n tussniwin talsanin (sciences humaines) deg tesdawit. Dgha iban dakk-n ddula tebgha d nettat kan ara ih’ekmen tasnakta (idéologie) sdaxel n tesdawit.
 
Seg yimir-nni, imeghnasen (militants) n tmazight âawden ṣ̣eggmen iman-nsen akk-n ad d-awin tikli ara idumen, yernu d ay-n kan ara yeffghen fell-asen. Dgha bdan la d-ssuffughen tisufagh (publications), ghas sâint ara ttesrih’, maca ddula ur tgi acemma akk-n ad teh’bes afraq-nsent, yernu tisufagh-a llant d ttawil ay yes sseddan yimeghnasen isalan (lexbarat) ilelliyen akk d weskasi-nsen (débat) ghef tekta (lfekrat) deg Tmurt n Leqbayel. Daghen, sbedden-d yimeghnasen tirebbaâ n leqdic ghef yinurar yerzan iles d yedles : dgha bdant trebbaâ-a la qeddcent ghef usseqâed n yiles amazigh (la d-bennun awalen itekniyen [techniques]), u ssawdhen ad d-ssuffghen iqeddicen yemmuzzgen (spécialisés), werjin ttwagan-d uqbel deg tmazight, am "Tmawalt n Tusnakt" (Léxique de mathématiques). Daghen, bdan yimeghnasen la ttgen timsirin (ddurhus) i usselmed n (tira) tmazight s tuffra. S way-a, qqlen yimeghnasen ur la ttnadin ara ad asen-d-tefk ddula kra, wanag llan la qeddcen yal ass akk-n ad d-bnun amussu (mouvement) ijehden ugar yernu d win ur nezmir ad yens : d idles amazigh ay izemren i yiman-is yernu yettuwehha gher yimal (avenir). D ay-a ay yejjan imeghnasen ad d-sbedden tasghunt (revue) Tafsut, ay yettwagan i lmend n tezrawin d weskasi (études et débats). Tafsut teqqel d ttawil ay deg aggagen (intellectuels) imazighen qqlen la d-ttarun ay-n ttxemmimen ghef temsal n yedles.
 
Daghen, yella mazal la d-yettili wembaddel gar waggagen (intellectuels) d wegdud deg Tmurt n Leqbayel; llant adtas n tegnatin ay deg ttemlilin am yibarazen (galas) d leqdicat ay d-yettilin ladgha deg tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu. Yugh lh’al, deg yiseggasen ay d-idhefren tafsut n 1980, tkemmel teddert tdukli-nni yellan gar waggagen d yegdud, u ay-a yettban-d s tmeskanin-nni (timesbaniyin) ay d-yellan deg yiseggasen n 1980, u ay deg tikkwal llan-d yimenghiyen meghghren gar yelmezsyen d yibulisen deg wakk timiwa n Tmurt n Leqbayel. Ghef umedya (lemtel), asmi ay ttwadttfen sebâa n yimeghnasen (militants) n tmazight deg Furharh n 1985, dindin kan kkren-d akk medden n Tmurt n Leqbayel (llant-d tmeskanin deg Tizi Wezzu, deg Bgayet, deg Yiâezszsugen, ...). Deg umezwaru n Nwemberh, ttwadttfen medden deg temsalt-nni n Temghunt tadzayrit n yizerfan n wemdan (Ligue algérienne des droits de l'homme), yili tamghunt-a llan la ttekkan deg-s yimeghnasen n tmazight s wadtas. D ay-n ay yessekren ccwal d ameqran u deg tgara, ixxamen n ccrheâ n tmiwa ay deg tekker h’ekmen-d lh’ebs i wazal n meyya n medden ghef ljal n ccwal.
 
Seg 1980 [gher 1990], nezmer ad d-nini dakk-n azal n 300 n medden ay yettucarhâen yernu yettwah’kem fell-asen lh’ebs ghef ljal n yimenghi ghef tmazight ama deg Tmurt n Leqbayel, ama deg Ldzayer tamaneght (attekki deg tmeskanin [timesbaniyin], afraq n tewriqin, attekki deg leqdicat d lecghal yeqqnen gher ussutter n tmazight). Ma d wid ay yettwadttfen sakk-in bran-asen-d mebla ma âeddan deg ccrheâ, wid yettwadttfen deg yexxamen n yibulisen, wid yettwah’ebsen tallit ghezzifen mebla ssebba, wid ay d-gherrqen seg yigherbazen (llakulat), wid umi kksen ipaspurhen-nsen u menâen-ten ad ffghen seg tmurt, wigi akk ur nezmir ad ten-id-neh’seb : tighawsiwin-a llant dherrunt-d yal ass, qqlent d tarutint ay nnummen akk yimeghnasen (militants) n tmazight. Dgha, ay-a akk yessnakay-agh-d amek ay tefka temsalt n tmazight izsuran deg wegdud deg Tmurt n Leqbayel, medden qqlen sskanayen-d s lejherh tamagit-nsen (identité) tamazight deg Tmurt n Leqbayel. Ghas ma tessukk ddula ach’al n yiseggasen n lh’erhs d weqmadh ghef wegdud, maca ay-a ur yessawedh ara ad yeqdheâ ay-n izedghen deg wulawen n medden. Ccwal yekkren deg 1985-1986 deg Tmurt n Leqbayel yella d win iweârhen ugar n win n 1980, u yessken-d dakk-n medden ukin-d deg tama-a, yernu amussu (mouvement) amazigh yessawedh ad d-yessuffegh urfan n medden gher lejherh u qqlen medden, ama deg tmurt n Ldzayer, ama deg umadhal (ddunit) slan s temsalt-a n tmazight u ttdhafaren-tt.

Lejnas steârhfen s ljehd n umussu* amazigh

*mouvement

D ay-n ibanen dakk-n amussu (mouvement) amazigh âawnen-t-id s wadtas yiminigen (ighriben) imazighen. Iminigen-a yekkan ach’al n yiseggasen deg lberhrhani yernu sâan ttejrhiba deg temsal n tsertit, d nitni ay iâawnen amussu ay yekkren deg tmurt n Leqbayel akk-n ad yemmager u ad yeṣ̣ber i weqmadh (répression) n ddula. Amussu amazigh yeqqel yesâa inedttaqen (porte-paroles) deg lgherba, d wid ay yellan la ttxebbiren lejnas ghef way-n la idherrun deg Tmurt n Leqbayel : seg 1980 d asawen, teqqel tghamsa (presse) la d-tessawadh isalan (lexbarat) n way-n idherrun deg Tmurt n Leqbayel ugar n zik. D ay-a ay yejjan ddula ur tesseqdac ara aqmadh (répression) ameqran deg Tmurt n Leqbayel u tuwey-d tikli ay deg th’uder imezdaghen n tama-a. D ay-a daghen ay yejjan medden ad qqlen ad ttarun negh ad ssawalen mebla akukru, mebla ma sneqsen ay-n ay ugaden ur as-iâejjeb ara i ddula, u d ay-a ay d-ikecfen aqmadh n ddula, u teqqel tneggarut-a ur tezmir ara ad teqmedh medden s tsusmi, ur isell yiwen, am zik-nni. Azal n âecrin n yiseggasen ay teqqim ddula, yinabadhen-ines (lh’ukumat) yemxallafen, la tqemmedh, la tettakel ghef yizerfan (lh’uquq) d tellyin, u tuwedh alama ay d asseqdec n uâetteb d tmenghiwt ! Akk-n ad tefk lh’eqq i yiman-is u ad teg lecghal-a akk, ddula tetth’arhab akk wid ay d-yekkren gher-s s yisem n Tegrawla (Révolution) yessuffghen Frhansa u s yisem n yimenghi mgal (contre) n temnukda (imprérialisme). Deg tallit-nni, llan medden yettwakren, ttwadttfen mebla lqanun, ttuâettben mebla ma yewlawel yiwen u mebla ma faqent trebbaâ tiberhrhaniyin yettnaghen ghef yizerfan (lh’uquq) n wemdan u ad d-lhunt s temsal-a.

Seg 1980 d asawen, ttuwehhant akk teftilin ghef Ldzayer, ladgha ghef Tmurt n Leqbayel : ay-n yebghu teg-it ddula akk-n ad teh’bes tikli n yisalan (lexbarat), ur tessawedh ara, medden akk zsran. Seg yimir-n, ddula teqqel tezsra dakk-n ur tezmir ara ad tkemmel aqmadh (répression) s tuffra.

Deg lweqt ay deg llant la d-dherrunt tedyanin deg tmurt, deg lgherba, imeghnasen bdan-d leqdic n wesh’ulfu (sensibilisation) d ussaki n medden, alama ay yeqqel umussu (mouvement) amazigh la d-ijebbed u la yettqenniâ Idzayriyen yellan deg lgherba ugar n Tdukli n Yidzayriyen deg Turhuft (Amicale des Algériens en Europe), yellan, deg tidet, d tarbaât itebâen gher FLN deg lberhrhani.

Daghen, deg tallit-nni, bdan wid yessawalen tamazight deg lgherba s timmad-nsen la d-ttarun idlisen ussnanen (scientifiques) ghef tmazight, dgha d ay-a ay yekkan iberhrhaniyen ad d-rren ugar lwelha-nsen gher way-n idherrun deg Tmurt n Leqbayel. Asmi ay bdan Yimazghanen (Maghrébins) la d-lehhun nitni s timmad-nsen s tezrawin (études) ghef tmazight, tebda la tettebâad takti-nni (lfekra) dakk-n d timura « listiâmerh » ara ijebbden lexyudh. Ay-n d-ttinin negh ttarun-t-id yimassanen-a (savants) imazghanen d ay-n zemren ad t-amnen medden, d nitni ara d-yessawalen ghef yiman-nsen, maci d wiyadh ara d-inedttqen deg umur-nsen. Imi ay d-lhan id-s yimazghanen (maghrébins) n tmura yemgerraden n Tefriqt n Ugafa, tebda « tmesmazight » (berbérisme) la tetteqqel d amussu (mouvement) n uxemmem ih’uzan akk tama-a, ur yeqqim ara kan deg yiwet n tmurt.

 
Timmuzgha* akk d tugdut

*amazighité

Ghas ma yella imussa isnaktanen (mouvement idéologiques) deg tmura n Tmazgha (Maghreb) mgerraden, maca tella yiwet n tghawsa ay ten-yesdukklen : Tamazgha d taârhabt yernu s kra n leqdic ara yettwagan ghef yedles, yessefk ad yeqqim kan deg tlisa-a. Ma d timmuzgha (amazighité), ya tettwankerh madhi, ya tettwah’qer alama ay d ay-n kan. Win yessawalen tamazight, imi ay yettwankerh am wakk-a, ur yessefk ara ad newhem mi ara t-nwali yettsughu-d : « Ala ! Lligh yernu mazal bghigh ad iligh azekka ! ». D ay-n ibanen ad d-yini ay-a, d lh’eqq-is.

D ay-n ibanen dakk-n ankarh akk d tririt-agi deg rrif d ay-n ara idhurren Amazigh s timmad-is, maca ay-a yezmer ad yili daghen d amihi (danger) i tmetti (société) s lekmal-is, imi, mi ara tessers ddula tilisa am tigi i yedles, ad teqqel tmughli n yedles d tamughli tuh’rhist, d tin ur nettazs gher sdat, d tin ur nqebbel wiyadh, d tin wesdukkel n bessif n wakk medden s ddaw n yiwet n tecdhadht, d tin ay deg ay-n ur tebghi ara ddula ad t-tekkes, ghas yella deg yedles, u d tin ay deg ttin ledwarh gar ddula d wegdud : deg lweqt ay deg idles d agdud ay t-id-yettgen, ad teqqel d ddula d nettat ara t-id-yettgen i wegdud. Skud ur werâad ur steârhfen ara yimezdaghen n Tmazgha (Maghreb) s wakk ay-n yellan deg tgemmi-nsen (patrimoine), werjin ad d-ffghen seg dhdheâfan d tiggunzsit tadelsant (sous-développement culturel). Ur yezmir ad d-yili wesnulfu wala tudert tadelsant n tidet mi ara tqeddec ddula akk-n ad ttun medden amezruy (ttarix) d yedles-nsen, mi ara d-th’ettem fell-asen (u ghef yiman-is) lh’eqq d umezruy n tkellax, mi ara tbennu azekka n tmetti (société) ghef tmucuha werjin nelli deg lweqt ay deg tejja ay-n yellan.

Ḍdheâfan ay yedhâef yedles deg tmura n Tmazgha (Maghreb) u ladgha deg Ldzayer d ay-n ay d-yurew wemnaâ ay ttwamenâent wadtas n tghawsiwin seg seg wasmi ay uwyent tmura-a izurag-nsent (indépendances) : tamazight teqqel deg rrif, maca daghen, tettuh’arheb tefrhensist yellan, ama nebgha negh negguma, d ttawil yughen azsar deg Tmazgha u d yiwen seg yilsawen igan leqran i yedles d ccfawat-nnegh. Ay-a yerra idles n tmura n Tmazgha d igellil, yernu qrib ulac akk tudert taggagt (intellectuelle) deg yimukan ay tedttef ddula. Axemmem yeddren, idles yeqqnen gher tidet ttafen kan iman-nsen berhrha i tsuda (institutions) n ddula, ttilin-d kan deg yimukan idergen i wallen n ddula, ladgha deg lberhrhani. Yagi, maci deg lbadtel ara naf dakk-n amur ameqran deg way-n d-itteffghen deg yedles d tudert taggagt (intellectuelle), itteffegh-d s tmazight negh s tefrhensist. Ay-a ur yebghi ara ad d-yini dakk-n taârhabt ur tezmir ara ad tesseddu idles amuddir, wanag ssebba nettat iles-a, deg tegnit ay deg nella, ata-n gar yifassen n d wid yedttfen tasertit (politique) d tesnakta (idéologie) n ddula.

Akk Imazghanen (Maghrébins), ama d wid yessawalen s tmazight negh d wid yessawalen s taârhabt, ala d rrbeh’ kan ara rebh’en lemmer ad h’esben timmuzgha d ah’ric seg wayla-nsen. Asmi ara mṣ̣alah’en Yimazghanen wagar-asen u ad qeblen tikkersit (complexité) d tendha (diversité) n tmagit (identité) d yedles-nsen, ass-nni, tezmer ad teqqel Tmazgha d tamurt n wesnulfu d unnerni. Tukci n wazal i tmazight d ay-n ara yesqeâden assaghen (relations) gar ugherman (citoyen) d ddula ay t-ih’ekmen. Amussu (mouvement) n tmazight d win ay d-yeglan yid-s s ussutter n tuggta (pluralisme), n weqbal n wiyadh, n tendha (diversité) akk d tlelli (liberté), ama d tin n wemdan, ama d tin n terbaât. Amussu-a yugi ad ttuh’ettmen medden ad ddren s ddaw n yiwet kan n tecdhadht, tin ara th’ettem fell-asen ddula u d tin ay izemren ad tghurr kra akk-n ad sbedden leh’kem amesbadtli. Tabrhat n umussu-a tban, ladgha deg Tmurt n Leqbayel : maci d ddula ara d-yesnulfun negh ara d-yebnun « idles » i wegdud, yernu ay-nni ur yelli d idles wanag d timucuha tunṣ̣ibin (officielles) ara qeblegh mebla ma nnigh-d acemma. S yisem-iw d agherman ilelli, ttalasegh ad d-inigh d acu ay lligh, d acu ay bghigh ad qqlegh u ad bnugh ay-a. Tamagit-inu (identité), idles-inu ur llin ara, akk-n ay d-yenna Kateb Yacine, d akaram (dossier) n lekwaghedh ay d-tga ddula, d win ay tettbeddil akk-n ay as-yehwa, ma d nekk ad qeblegh ay-n s tsusmi. Idles d ay-n ay d-tesnulfuy yal ass tmetti (société) tilellit.

Ghef way-a, amussu (mouvement) amazigh ur yelli d win ay yes bghan Yimazighen ad ghelqen ghef yiman-nsen, d amussu uh’rhis yerzan kan kra n wegdud, negh d taghelnazsri (nationalisme) tamaynut am tid-n akk yekkan : wanag, assutter amazigh d win ay d-yuwyen taghawsa tamaynut, d tin ay yugaren iâeddan i tlisa n tmazight-nni s timmad-is, d assirem i lebni n tmetti (société) ay deg tella tendha (diversité), ay deg medden mṣ̣alah’en wagar-asen yernu maci d amnaâ, ah’qar d wenkarh ara yesseddayen tighawsiwin n tmurt. Ad tili tlelli tadelsant (culturelle) d tlelli i yiles amazigh, maca daghen ad tili tlelli i wakk medden, acku wid yessawalen tamazight fehmen dakk-n ur zmiren ara ad ttwadhemnen yizerfan-nsen (lh’uquq) s tidet u ad dumen deg yiwet tmetti (société) ala ma yella d agherman (citoyen) ara yedttfen leh’kem yernu amdan ur itteqqel ara ittedder u itteddu akk-n ay as-yehwa i ddula negh i kra n terbaât yerran leh’kem d ayla-s.

Yettwakkes-d seg « Imazighen ass-a », n Salem Chaker (tizsrigin Bouchène, Ldzayer, 1990).

